@startuml

title review diff style legend template

top to bottom direction
hide methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 90
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<existing>> #F7F9FC
    BorderColor<<existing>> #546E7A
    FontColor<<existing>> #243447
    BackgroundColor<<added>> #EEF9EF
    BorderColor<<added>> #2E7D32
    FontColor<<added>> #1B5E20
    BackgroundColor<<removed>> #FFF1F1
    BorderColor<<removed>> #C62828
    FontColor<<removed>> #7F1D1D
    BackgroundColor<<changed>> #FFF8E1
    BorderColor<<changed>> #F9A825
    FontColor<<changed>> #4E342E
    BackgroundColor<<risk>> #F4F7FA
    BorderColor<<risk>> #607D8B
    FontColor<<risk>> #1F2933
}

legend bottom right
    |= Style |= Meaning |
    |<#F7F9FC> existing | unchanged source of truth |
    |<#EEF9EF> added | new element or new route |
    |<#FFF1F1> removed | deleted or retired element |
    |<#FFF8E1> changed | behavior or responsibility changed |
    |<#F4F7FA> risk | review note, constraint, or split reason |
endlegend

package "copy this style and legend" as StyleLegendTemplate {
    class "Existing" as Existing <<existing>>
    class "Added" as Added <<added>>
    class "Removed" as Removed <<removed>>
    class "Changed" as Changed <<changed>>
    class "Risk / Note" as RiskNote <<risk>>
}

Existing -[#546E7A]-> Changed : kept dependency
Added -[#2E7D32,dashed]-> Changed : new path
Removed -[#C62828,dashed]-> Changed : removed path
RiskNote -[#607D8B,dotted]-> Changed : review note

@enduml
